---
import CompanyLayout from "../layouts/CompanyLayout.astro";
---

<CompanyLayout>
  <Fragment slot="overview">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-700 mb-4">
      Privacy Policy for VMLSoft
    </h1>

    <section class="space-y-6">
      <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> July 25, 2025</p>
      <p>
        This Privacy Policy describes how your personal information is handled
        by VMLSoft ("we", "us", or "our") when you visit our website <a
          data-goatcounter-click="nav_home"
          data-goatcounter-title="Navigation: Home"
          href="https://vmlsoft.com"
          class="text-blue-600 underline">https://vmlsoft.com</a
        >.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">1. No Cookies or Tracking</h2>
      <p>
        We do not use cookies, analytics tools, or tracking scripts on this
        website. Your browsing experience is private and not monitored by us.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">2. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>
        We only collect personal information that you voluntarily provide
        through direct contact (e.g., when emailing us or filling out a contact
        form).
      </p>
      <p>This may include:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
        <li>Your name</li>
        <li>Email address</li>
        <li>Any information you include in your message or request</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">
        3. How We Use Your Information
      </h2>
      <p>
        Any information you share with us is used solely to respond to your
        inquiry, provide services you've requested, or manage our business
        relationship.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">4. Data Sharing</h2>
      <p>
        We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal data. Your information may
        only be shared:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
        <li>With your explicit consent</li>
        <li>If legally required by Danish or EU authorities</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">5. Data Storage</h2>
      <p>
        We retain your information only as long as necessary to fulfill the
        purpose of communication or service, unless a longer retention period is
        required by law.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">6. Your Rights (GDPR)</h2>
      <p>
        If you are located in the European Economic Area (EEA), you have rights
        under GDPR:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
        <li>Access your personal data</li>
        <li>Request correction or deletion</li>
        <li>Restrict or object to processing</li>
        <li>Data portability</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        To exercise any of these rights, contact us at <a
          data-goatcounter-click="nav_email"
          data-goatcounter-title="Navigation: Email"
          href="mailto:contact@vmlsoft.com"
          class="text-blue-600 underline">contact@vmlsoft.com</a
        >.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">7. External Links</h2>
      <p>
        Our website may link to external sites (e.g., GitHub, LinkedIn). We are
        not responsible for their privacy practices. Please review their privacy
        policies separately.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6">8. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, you can reach us at:
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Email:</strong>
        <a
          data-goatcounter-click="nav_email"
          data-goatcounter-title="Navigation: Email"
          href="mailto:contact@vmlsoft.com"
          class="text-blue-600 underline">contact@vmlsoft.com</a
        >
      </p>
    </section>
  </Fragment>

  <Fragment slot="about">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-700 mb-2">Company Info</h2>
    <p class="mb-0">VMLSoft - CVR: 44585596</p>
    <p>Based in Denmark. GDPR-compliant. Invoice-ready.</p>
  </Fragment>
</CompanyLayout>
